commit.message:
configure.ac (libtool_VERSION): To 6:11:0.


2008-03-18  Benjamin Kosnik  <bkoz@redhat.com>

	* configure.ac (libtool_VERSION): To 6:11:0.
	* configure: Regenerate.
	* aclocal.m4: Regenerate.

From-SVN: r133317
